Title: Abra Cadaver
Plot: Grissom investigates when a woman vanishes while taking part in a magician's act. A rock star's death on a band bus appears to be the result of an overdose, but Catherine uncovers evidence that points to murder.
GuestStars: Lawrence Monoson, Tom Noonan, Jennifer Sky, Jon Sklaroff, Esteban Powell, Catherine Grace, Sven Holmberg, Blumes Tracy, Jack McGee, Tushka Bergen, Salvator Xuereb, Jack McGee
